"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:03:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問香港堆行業有咩咁巴閉兩年就唔同晒？唔講仲以為佢講緊科技行業，香港得服務業為主可以點變？佢個所謂個市場變化咪只係需求減弱，零售業價量齊跌，呢個唔算係行業本身出現變化，TVB拍劇就已經同兩年前冇分別啦，兩年講到成個行業upgrade左咁，笑撚死人，呢班HR成日好似保藥黨咁夾埋僱主玩班打工仔</blockquote><br />\n個d HR 呃學生哥就得<br />\n個變化只係生意額下跌, 而且名店sales 大多數稱唔上專業, 只係跟公司training 上堂, 背熟d 資料就得, 毫無專業可言."},{"pid":"69a041adcb8ecd44d312f8e5c424027b87db9edb","tid":194647,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:04:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a37d16086e9b8cacb3cc555be7e603358020e67","tid":194647,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/150621_51e4c3244e58d22d8d0fc03cf41f645e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F150621_51e4c3244e58d22d8d0fc03cf41f645e.jpg&h=b7b298a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由working holiday轉working visa<br />\n人工由香港萬幾到澳洲5萬幾，點睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9a522e0feea40e3e7fc232b956f418e59b1d18","tid":194647,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Working holiday中<br />\n搭晒路唔會返嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做緊咩工?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n酒店</blockquote><br />\n f&amp;b? <br />\n咩部門?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩都會畀我做下<br />\n間唔中會調下職位<br />\nOffice裡面做下啲clerk嘢都有<br />\n不過主要係因為呢邊有屋企人居留<br />\nWorking holiday只係我決定離開香港嘅搭腳石<br />\n長遠會同屋企人一齊發展"},{"pid":"988458206514a111135ea03ecd600d159ba974c5","tid":194647,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:10:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/150621_51e4c3244e58d22d8d0fc03cf41f645e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F150621_51e4c3244e58d22d8d0fc03cf41f645e.jpg&h=b7b298a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由working holiday轉working visa<br />\n人工由香港萬幾到澳洲5萬幾，點睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳洲公司用457請我過去, 之後我自己唔做返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4b281a910d8e40fc1cbc068bd837af3414e09d","tid":194647,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/10/150621_51e4c3244e58d22d8d0fc03cf41f645e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2F150621_51e4c3244e58d22d8d0fc03cf41f645e.jpg&h=b7b298a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由working holiday轉working visa<br />\n人工由香港萬幾到澳洲5萬幾，點睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳洲公司用457請我過去, 之後我自己唔做返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解<br />\n睇見林鄭做特首都唔想返香港喎<br />\n做兩年轉pr移民好過啦"},{"pid":"235d39c4ade03482328f21bbc7d2010f676b294f","tid":194647,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:16:44.000Z","msg":"周綺萍妳因住有報應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230bebbc05543f9ba7363855f6e921af95f5ce59","tid":194647,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n點解<br />\n睇見林鄭做特首都唔想返香港喎<br />